==English==

===Etymology===
From [[cyclic]], meaning of a circle.

===Noun===
'''[[cyclic]] [[quadrilateral]]'''

# (''Geometry'') A [[quadrilateral]] whose [[vertex|vertices]] all intersect a single [[circle]].

